headline: How Recent Moves Are Rewriting The Story For Archer Daniels Midland ADM
summary: Archer Daniels Midland just saw its fair value estimate edge to about US$57.09 per share, a very small change that keeps the stock in roughly the same price range even as the story around its earnings outlook becomes more debated. With Q3 earnings ahead of estimates and a fresh US$59 price target from JPMorgan, the latest update reflects a balance between support from recent results and caution around profit headwinds that analysts continue to flag.
